{"tid":1997473,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"黃藍是政見 時代時良知","createTime":"2020-05-01T16:29:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T08:44:11.000Z","uid":222513,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a85b58d48a53567193879c2617eedb7061ba4fe4","tid":1997473,"uid":222513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T16:29:24.000Z","msg":"成年以黎都差唔多幫襯咗70間黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n時代冰室都幫襯咗3次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能因為香港地做飲食縮水又走精面 以前都麻麻茶餐廳<br />\n但發現蕭生好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">冬瓜鴨腿湯飯</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> sor9ry 淨係影咗一半 成碗上黎嚇死人好大兜 鴨腿超大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AwR2Fbt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAwR2Fbt.jpg&h=27e2af62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">麻辣口水雞</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個超驚喜 啲雞有三層咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個辣汁麻而不辣係點做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食起黎舒服但個嘴又麻 10分過癮 有菜之餘仲有泡菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個飯仲要係雞油飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家外賣9折 例湯照有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 蕭生完全係痴撚曬線 個雞可以分兩餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲麻辣汁留返黎點皮蛋 $50可以食一日三餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eAyXt5s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeAyXt5s.jpg&h=ff9eacba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">鰻魚炒飯</span>：好香不過不失<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xjk66QY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxjk66QY.jpg&h=6b96a32d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c5089b23bbb8428908e53eabf084fe8a9e46ca89","tid":1997473,"uid":76365,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T16:33:26.000Z","msg":"深夜po美食圖<br />\n你好殘忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1abc30ea598f94638c33417d4fbc79f10728d923","tid":1997473,"uid":129042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T16:34:44.000Z","msg":"平時一個人淨係食咖喱<br />\n一班朋友嘅話就去食小菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67d30df4345de9344dd79a49606f3ef35e4a803f","tid":1997473,"uid":222513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5089b23bbb8428908e53eabf084fe8a9e46ca89","tid":1997473,"uid":76365,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T16:33:26.000Z","msg":"深夜po美食圖<br />\n你好殘忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T16:34:53.000Z","msg":"Sor9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見到無啦9有人屌時代冰室忍唔住開"},{"pid":"fdec0138a969c331f453b4a1de39931214a65435","tid":1997473,"uid":129042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67d30df4345de9344dd79a49606f3ef35e4a803f","tid":1997473,"uid":222513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5089b23bbb8428908e53eabf084fe8a9e46ca89","tid":1997473,"uid":76365,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T16:33:26.000Z","msg":"深夜po美食圖<br />\n你好殘忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T16:34:53.000Z","msg":"Sor9<img src=\